data.description: Privacy, seclusion and acreage just 30 minutes from Portland and Hillsboro. This daylight ranch offers beautiful wood floors, updated kitchen, 3 bedrooms and two baths on the accessible main floor and an abundance of extra square footage in the completed finished basement that opens to the back patio and beautiful forest. This is a wonderful property where you can see the seasons change and relax in your own private oasis.
